Prolog Module geaendert:

AnswerTransformator.pro              FragmentToPropositions.pro           PropositionProcessor.pro
BDMCompile.pro                       GeneralUtilities.pro                 QAmanager.pro
BDMEvaluation.pro                    IpcChannel.pro                       QueryProcessor.pro
BDMForget.pro                        IpcParser.pro                        SMLaxioms.pro
BDMIntegrityChecker.pro              LTstubs.pro                          ScanFormatUtilities.pro
BDMKBMS.pro                          LanguageInterface.pro                SelectExpressions.pro
BIM2C.pro                            Literals.pro                         SemanticIntegrity.pro
CBserverInterface.pro                MSFOLassertionParserUtilities.pro    TriggerGenerator.pro
